formulas.name: Formula_Lease_Assignment_Text
formulas.expression: IF({!$Record.Lease_Assignment__c}==True, "Please also note that the room you are moving into was previously occupied by another tenant, which is why you will be asked to sign an assignment agreement. The original lease to which you are assigning will be sent in a separate email for your reference. You will only be financially responsible for rent payments during your occupancy term, as detailed in your membership agreement.", " ")

formulas.name: FormulaMonthsToOpening
formulas.expression: IF( OR( ISBLANK({!$Record.Expected_Home_Open_Date_new__c}) , ( {!$Record.Expected_Home_Open_Date_new__c} - Today()) < 0 ) , null , IF( YEAR({!$Record.Expected_Home_Open_Date_new__c}) = YEAR(TODAY()), MONTH({!$Record.Expected_Home_Open_Date_new__c}) - MONTH(TODAY()), FLOOR(({!$Record.Expected_Home_Open_Date_new__c} - TODAY()) / 30.25) ) )
